Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.53,0:00:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小紬的眉毛很浓密呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.98,0:00:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.27,0:00:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.02,0:00:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腌萝卜哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.64,0:00:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.68,0:00:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.76,0:00:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腌萝卜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.68,0:00:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和尚？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.15,0:00:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来还是烧得不轻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.56,0:00:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.61,0:00:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感冒了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.53,0:00:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忧…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.10,0:00:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  「哼」一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.91,0:00:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  忧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.71,0:00:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会和学校联系的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.97,0:00:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.39,0:00:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要迟到了呢  忧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.68,0:00:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.30,0:01:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰箱里有冰激凌和橘子果冻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.09,0:01:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要哈根达斯#￥%&…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.01,0:01:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.45,0:01:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事的话就用手机联系我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.46,0:01:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.20,0:01:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.22,0:02:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烧还没有退啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.50,0:02:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以现在的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.86,0:02:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计明天也…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.51,0:02:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有四天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.64,0:03:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我能替她生病就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.40,0:03:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让感冒转移到我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.85,0:03:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么转移啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.48,0:03:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如…嘴对嘴喂饭之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.24,0:03:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是开放的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.80,0:03:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.39,0:03:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要吓到学妹们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.05,0:03:18.05,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终话  轻音！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.50,0:03:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.45,0:03:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.44,0:03:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然在这种时候感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.52,0:03:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是散漫的证据啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.98,0:03:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你传染给她的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.85,0:03:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？ 是我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.16,0:03:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  想想前后的时间差距
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.02,0:03:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不过可能是前一段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.29,0:03:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这里面选一下登台服装吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.90,0:03:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强制啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.26,0:03:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候准备了那么多…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.01,0:03:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪一件都可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.70,0:03:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说这件
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.70,0:03:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女服务生服~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.71,0:03:46.45,small,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.91,0:03:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.49,0:03:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更加不要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.57,0:03:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这个可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.12,0:03:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  总觉得越来越有趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.19,0:03:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.61,0:03:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪清醒点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.52,0:04:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  看啊看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.46,0:04:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.72,0:04:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个很可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.56,0:04:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.44,0:04:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且活动起来也蛮方便的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.04,0:04:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  那就这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.72,0:04:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶吶  就选这件吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.83,0:04:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选这件吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.88,0:04:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选这件吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.48,0:04:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐很中意那件衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.67,0:04:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以整整一天都穿着浴衣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.87,0:04:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能着凉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.48,0:04:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是小学生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.76,0:04:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很像唯前辈的作风呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.17,0:04:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.92,0:04:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件衣服虽然看起来还过得去  不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.94,0:04:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静地想想  穿着那种衣服会害羞的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.09,0:04:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧  澪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.63,0:04:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.75,0:04:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天开始能不能练习一下主音旋律？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.60,0:04:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.70,0:04:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怕唯可能会赶不上演出吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.63,0:04:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.71,0:04:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是为了以防万一罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.83,0:04:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那放学后见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.99,0:04:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.23,0:04:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.30,0:04:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.79,0:05:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一碗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.92,0:05:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.57,0:05:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.20,0:05:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.71,0:05:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓  能行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.54,0:05:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩  还过得去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.10,0:05:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那从头再来一遍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.97,0:05:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.05,0:05:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.04,0:05:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.28,0:05:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感冒已经好了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.68,0:05:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  感冒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.80,0:05:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咳咳…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.16,0:05:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是故意的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.61,0:05:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  也就是说已经没事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.27,0:05:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊  病好了的话早上也要来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.68,0:05:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很担心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.74,0:05:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.07,0:06:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  是在放学的时候突然好了的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.86,0:06:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是不想上课吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.30,0:06:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了算了  我们快点练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.72,0:06:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.23,0:06:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.52,0:06:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锵~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.79,0:06:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.45,0:06:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.51,0:06:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.90,0:06:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是偶然吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.72,0:06:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我多心了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.17,0:06:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.62,0:06:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.21,0:06:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.68,0:06:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.46,0:06:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.21,0:06:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,配合的太完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.81,0:06:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今为止都没有这样的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.89,0:06:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯的旋律控制得太准了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.29,0:06:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.45,0:06:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都没…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.00,0:06:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月亮好红啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.28,0:06:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是很好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.38,0:06:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完美地配合起来不就好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.37,0:06:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得很舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.88,0:06:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.96,0:06:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像小梓说的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.24,0:06:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.74,0:06:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下子有些混乱了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.57,0:07:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律前辈和紬前辈担心过头了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.28,0:07:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律前辈？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.83,0:07:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紬前辈？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.23,0:07:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.09,0:07:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也该适可而止了吧  小忧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.65,0:07:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么时候来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.72,0:07:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是……小忧?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.31,0:07:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使瞒过了大家的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.00,0:07:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也瞒不过我的双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.23,0:07:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的胸部比小唯的大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.49,0:07:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你在说什么啊  我完全不明白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.40,0:07:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那叫一下我的昵称
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.04,0:07:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓…梓2号
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.41,0:07:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冒牌货
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.04,0:07:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.50,0:07:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来还真是像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.75,0:07:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都没有发觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.66,0:07:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过话说回来  小忧会弹吉他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.70,0:07:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.25,0:07:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是姐姐让我碰了几次吉他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.35,0:07:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样弹的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.99,0:07:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有写着哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.16,0:07:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这都可以啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.19,0:07:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话还是让唯一直休息着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.23,0:07:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.28,0:07:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梓  对不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.99,0:07:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.39,0:08:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着躺在床上的姐姐  我有些坐立不安…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.94,0:08:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.22,0:08:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好熟悉的场景
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.21,0:08:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.09,0:08:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起哦  让你们担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.23,0:08:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.48,0:08:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.37,0:08:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚起来之后就不知为何觉得变精神了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.08,0:08:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算稍微来练习…阿嚏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.69,0:08:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好脏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.87,0:08:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说  已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.56,0:08:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.55,0:08:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我也要纸巾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.03,0:08:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  吉太~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.07,0:08:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.38,0:08:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我抱…好重
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.21,0:08:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.55,0:08:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次给我当茶点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.40,0:08:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.32,0:08:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烧一点都没有退啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.32,0:08:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.96,0:08:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然硬撑不行啊  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.10,0:08:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正式表演时还是不算上我比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.89,0:09:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.45,0:09:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵  吉他演奏就交给你了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.07,0:09:07.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.54,0:09:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.55,0:09:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  要是不能大家一起演出还不如就不演了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.58,0:09:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  梓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.90,0:09:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯  正式表演之前不准再来轻音部了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.79,0:09:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终…终于下了禁令吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.97,0:09:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是你想的那样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.14,0:09:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到正式演出前  好好休息把感冒治好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.30,0:09:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后大家一起迎接演出
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.34,0:09:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前绝不要放弃  明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.44,0:09:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.42,0:09:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓也要好好练习
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.87,0:09:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是为了替补唯  而是为了今后的表演
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.57,0:09:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.71,0:09:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家加油做好自己现在能做到的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.74,0:09:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.45,0:10:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  晚安了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.69,0:10:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.49,0:10:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要好好睡觉  现在我能做的就是加油睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.57,0:10:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要赶在演出前好起来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.63,0:10:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯  没来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.51,0:10:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手机打了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.95,0:10:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来过短信了  说是一定会赶上的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.18,0:10:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,12点半了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.66,0:10:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要再温习一遍？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.22,0:10:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把唯的演奏部分忽略
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.69,0:10:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.61,0:10:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.49,0:10:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样没有唯前辈的演出也没有任何意义
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.26,0:11:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.77,0:11:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞台延迟了10分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.80,0:11:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还是按原计划下午1点就开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.20,0:11:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.98,0:11:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人都到齐了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.19,0:11:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻音部出演者全体准备完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.02,0:11:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小和
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.56,0:11:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前发生过这样的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.70,0:11:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经装满了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.73,0:11:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.06,0:11:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是用这个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.52,0:12:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.51,0:12:03.39,small,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.23,0:12:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  小唯啊  欢迎来玩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.65,0:12:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.08,0:12:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是啥事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.20,0:12:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从以前开始就是个怪人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.90,0:12:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是为什么讲这件事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.18,0:12:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从以前开始  只要有着迷的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.90,0:12:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯就非常的专注
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.56,0:12:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一定会忘记感冒的  所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.98,0:12:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.34,0:12:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意一下这气氛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.68,0:12:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说你最近都干什么去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.26,0:12:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都忙得不可开交呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.94,0:12:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀  当然没有虚度时日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.62,0:12:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考虑到温度的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.19,0:12:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对之前的浴衣进行改良  做了防寒式
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.13,0:12:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希望你能把那份热情用在别的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.91,0:12:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是那改良版
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.59,0:12:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.63,0:13:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.77,0:13:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然来学校了  就马上到这儿来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.92,0:13:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.91,0:13:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.13,0:13:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太过分了  大家这么担心你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.68,0:13:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.15,0:13:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好弥补一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.02,0:13:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梓可是最担心你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.88,0:13:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.08,0:13:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.61,0:13:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是让人没办法  而且感冒的时候就应该…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.50,0:13:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.58,0:13:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵  对不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.41,0:13:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.44,0:13:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会拼命加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.53,0:13:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和大家一起加油  别生气了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.50,0:13:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来一场最好的演出吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.01,0:13:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你没办法  就特别原谅你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.56,0:13:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和好的证明  亲一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.66,0:13:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的有担心我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.95,0:13:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.84,0:14:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  到时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.43,0:14:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家去会馆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.67,0:14:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.18,0:14:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  吉太呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.63,0:14:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应该放在这儿了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.28,0:14:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个被小忧带回去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.41,0:14:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  吉他我放这儿了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.02,0:14:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  谢谢啊  忧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.33,0:14:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起来了  怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.96,0:14:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.87,0:14:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐和酱老师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.59,0:14:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.29,0:14:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不是吉太没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.89,0:14:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.58,0:14:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会弹除了吉太以外其他的吉他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.63,0:14:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.30,0:14:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.90,0:14:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.15,0:14:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害啊  已经坐满人了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.21,0:14:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在这儿看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.43,0:14:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小忧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.87,0:14:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  又见面了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.02,0:14:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年的结尾太精彩了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.63,0:15:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是轻音部「放学后的下午茶时间」乐队的演出
